'''Wisdom Wiz Kudowor ('''wɔ woo no September da ɛtɔ so 19, afe 1957) yɛ mfoni ho dwumadifo a ofiri [[Ghana]] man mu.

Kudowor nyaa sukuu pɔn ho kyɛfa wɔ suapɔn a ɛne College of Art, University of Science and Technology, Ghana . ɔde n’adesua baa awie  wɔ afe 1981 a na ɔne odikanfo wɔ mfoniho dwumadie mu

.W’ahyehyɛ nneɛma pii wɔ Ghana man mu a emu baako ne mfoni ɛwɔ Kwame Nkrumah Memorial Park. Ne nwuma da adi wɔ ankorɛankore ne amansan nyinaa mu a emu bi nea ɛwɔ Artists Alliance Gallery a ɛwɔ Labadi, Accra.

